WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:19.380
Spin. Self play, fine tuning that improves LLMs. Trixie. It's a form of fast inference involving sparsity. PHY2 is a model from Microsoft. Lightning Attention 2 is an alternative to Flash Attention. Mixtral 8x7B.

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:45.000
This is a mixture of Expert's model. Solar 10.7B is a Mixtral model with some extra layers added in. OpenChat is a fine tune of the Mixtral model. Nultux 8x7B V1. This is a version of the Mixtral model, fine tuned.

00:00:45.800 --> 00:01:05.190
Gemini Pro is Google's best model, or perhaps not as good as Gemini Ultra. Microsoft PHY2, I've already mentioned. Desi LM is a high speed 7B model. That's Desi LM 7B. Arena Elo is a means of comparing LLMs.

00:01:05.190 --> 00:01:24.260
MT Bench is another metric and MM LU is also. GPT-4 Turbo is a fast GPT-4 model by OpenAI. Mixtral Medium is a mixture of Expert's but with larger Expert's. Then Mixtral 8x7B.

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:45.380
Clod 1. Clod 2. Clod 2.0 are the latest Clod models. Mixtral 8x7B Instruct V1, or rather V01. That's Mixtral 8x7B Instruct V0.1. That's the latest mixture of Expert's.

00:01:46.320 --> 00:02:06.160
Yi34B Chat is a very strong fine tune of LLMA. Clod Instant 1 is one of the Clod models. TuLU2 DPO 70B is a DPO fine tuned model by Allen AI. It's a fine tune of the LLMA 2 model, the 70B.

00:02:06.920 --> 00:02:12.380
Wizard LM 70B is also a fine tune of the LLMA 70B model.

